@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Switch: invatare tabela CAM (concept)

[Host A\nMAC_A] as A
[Host B\nMAC_B] as B
[Host C\nMAC_C] as C
[Switch] as SW

A -- SW
B -- SW
C -- SW

note right of SW
  1) Cand primeste un cadru
     invata: MAC_sursa -> port
  2) Daca MAC_dest e cunoscut:
     trimite doar pe portul respectiv
  3) Daca nu e cunoscut:
     flood pe celelalte porturi
end note
@enduml
